            <abstract>
                <p>Short poem, probably to Kiros, which is attested in one stanza in <ref type="mss" corresp="ESdmd013"/> and in two stanzas 
                in <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient567"/>. It is not clear whether the version in two stanzas is constituted of
                    two originally independent texts, 
                the first being dedicated to Kiros and the second to Rufāʾel, that were then conflated.</p>
            </abstract>
